The iPhone 16 impresses with a powerful A18 chip, improved cooling, the new 48MP camera, and an Action Button—making the base model a strong contender for buyers this year. The Apple Watch Series 10 boasts a stunning titanium finish and cutting-edge display tech, making it sleeker and brighter.
